1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
(Six months later)

2
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:08,840
Hinata.

3
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:09,880
Yes!

4
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:11,590
Are you settling in okay?

5
00:00:11,590 --> 00:00:13,300
Want to tag along on a sales call?

6
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:15,100
Really? Can I?

7
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:16,730
Get ready. We're heading out.

8
00:00:16,730 --> 00:00:17,930
Right away!

9
00:00:24,690 --> 00:00:27,740
Wow, Kamiki-san,
you really live up to your reputation!

10
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:32,530
Even the president of Takeshita shoji
signed on!

11
00:00:32,530 --> 00:00:33,580
That was amazing!

12
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:35,790
The materials you prepared really helped.

13
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:40,080
No, I just did exactly
what you told me to do, Kamiki-san.

14
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:46,170
Kamiki-san,
we want to do business with you.

15
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:49,880
We only agreed
because it's you.

16
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:52,010
Kamiki.

17
00:00:52,010 --> 00:00:52,800
Whoa!

18
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:54,100
Watch out!
